{"tid":175185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"血淋淋截肢相都分享？ 醫院怒炒靚女實習醫生","createTime":"2017-03-27T10:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T15:41:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d1b63727cacafae8b41fb7f36bc3a3741856d6","tid":175185,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">血淋淋截肢相都分享？醫院怒炒靚女實習醫生<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170326/19970482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170326%2F19970482&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=6f16d58b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170326%2F19970482&h=c220ebfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170326/19970482</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥兩名女實習醫生，在參與手術後竟然拿著病人的截肢和看似是胃的內臟合照，並上載到社交網站Twitter，結果被院方解僱，當局還會向法院正式提出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名實習醫生是24歲的嘉西雅(Carolina Dominguez Garcia)，她滿面笑容拿著一隻截除的腳掌拍照，再上載Twitter，並寫著：「爸爸，我的第一隻小腿，若這些照片令你不安，抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，嘉西雅除了與病人的截肢合照，亦拿著一塊似乎是胃的物體來拍照。暫時未知該截肢與內臟屬哪位病人或他們的家人會否提控。<br />\n<br />\n事件中兩位實習醫生在墨西哥北部蒙特雷(Monterrey)一間醫院工作。該市的社會保障部主管亞里奧拿(Mikel Arriola)知悉事件後，立刻把她們解僱，並宣佈會向法院投訴。他說，兩名實習醫生把不恰當的照片上載社交網站。<br />\n<br />\n一位網民回應事件時說：「事件顯示你需為你的愚蠢付出代價。」不過另一位網民說：「我認為警告已足夠，毋須公開羞辱。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"444c1ef30018fe1d4db0b54f174b8fdf16fb25aa","tid":175185,"uid":42293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"no pic?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cdf25be485449bc4d801199007b7ff4adb5be3","tid":175185,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"pure text discussion <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63e00722f390018c5c28e5bbde7f1412131375b","tid":175185,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"社交網絡已經令人類毫無道德可言"},{"pid":"e5f1d9195969c990f31992bcee2422e4176fa9aa","tid":175185,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社交網絡已經令人類毫無道德可言</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d396ce50ff9f5d65c7adcd146807f9e25fb8cc43","tid":175185,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"又無靚女<br />\n又無截肢&hellip;"}]}